      *------------------------------------------------------
      *  INITIALIZE
      *------------------------------------------------------
     C           *INZSR    BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@END   1
TCH62C                     PARM           @OUTQ
      *
     C           K#IZAP    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           D@ZAIS
     C                     KFLD           D@ZAIK
     C           K#ADGP    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@YY
     C                     KFLD           K@MM
     C                     KFLD           K@DD
